22 SECTION 1. Arkansas Code Title 14, Chapter 14, Subchapter 12, is
23 amended to add an additional section to read as follows:
24 14-14-1214. Compensation of sheriffs.
25 (a) A quorum court shall fix by ordinance the annual salary of the
26 sheriff as provided under § 14-14-1204 subject to the adjustments provided by
27 § 14-14-1210 or otherwise provided by law.
28 (b) If an individual elected or appointed to the office of sheriff
29 does not have the training or experience provided under § 14-14-1315(a)(1) or
30 § 14-14-1315(a)(2) as documented on the filing required under § 14-14-1315,
31 the quorum court shall fix by ordinance the annual salary of the sheriff at
32 the minimum provided by § 14-14-1204, subject to the adjustments provided by
33 § 14-14-1210.
